  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>気がついたら、けっこう長く旅してるよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>By the time I realized it, it look like
we've been traveling for a while now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほんと、こんなに長い冒険になるなんて、
家を出る時は思わなかったよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Indeed. I, myself, would never have thought that
this adventure would take ages when I left home.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46112</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、オレが言った通り、外の世界って楽しいだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So...? Aren't I right? The outside world is super fun!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46176</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Coorooro!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、この旅いつまで続くんだろ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...How long are we going to keep traveling?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おらは、このままでも全然構わんだーよ。
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;と、ずっと一緒にいられるだど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, personally I do not mind this at all!
I'm happy as long as I'm by &lt;Mel&gt;'s side.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっかぁ、アルベルトもずーっと一緒だったもんね。
でも、もしボクらの目的が終わったらどうするの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh right. You've always been with us haven't you, Albert?
But, what do you plan on doing once our trip's ended?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46632</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そりゃ、ノルンんとこに帰んだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Duh, he's going back to Norn, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46780</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>未来の事は、おらにもわからねーだーよ。
ただひとつ言えるのは、おらにも夢があるっちゅーことだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even I do not know about my future.
One thing's for sure, I have my own dreams too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>アルベルトさんの、夢？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You do?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47024</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;と一緒にいられるようにとか、いっぱい
あるだが、おらが、おらとしていられる存在意義ってもんが重要だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, I have a lot of things I want to do with you, but
what's important is why I am myself.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へへ、じゃあ、タンスとして生涯を閉じるってことか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ohh...So you wanna make it out there as a closet?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_205_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………い、いや、はぅ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>N-No...Hah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
